    {
      "id": "PopularPost363968",
      "post_content": "Magical Hack, and its counterpart [Sleight of Mind](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sleight of Mind), were best used with the color-hosers that were so prevalent back then. [Lifetap](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lifetap) and [Volcanic Eruption](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Volcanic Eruption) were made that much better when Magical Hack could make them effective against any opponent. You could change your [Lord of Atlantis](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lord of Atlantis) to give all your [Merfolk of the Pearl Trident](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Merfolk of the Pearl Trident) forestwalk. Also, because it didn't say \"all instances\" at the time, one could use it to allow his [Sea Serpent](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sea Serpent) or [Island Fish Jasconius](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Island Fish Jasconius) to attack a person who controlled Mountains without worrying about his islandhome creature being buried. And you could do all that without ever leaving blue!",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost363968\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">Magical Hack, and its counterpart <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sleight of Mind\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sleight of Mind\">Sleight of Mind</a>, were best used with the color-hosers that were so prevalent back then.  <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lifetap\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lifetap\">Lifetap</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Volcanic Eruption\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Volcanic Eruption\">Volcanic Eruption</a> were made that much better when Magical Hack could make them effective against any opponent.  You could change your <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lord of Atlantis\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lord of Atlantis\">Lord of Atlantis</a> to give all your <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Merfolk of the Pearl Trident\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Merfolk of the Pearl Trident\">Merfolk of the Pearl Trident</a> forestwalk.  Also, because it didn't say \"all instances\" at the time, one could use it to allow his <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sea Serpent\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sea Serpent\">Sea Serpent</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Island Fish Jasconius\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Island Fish Jasconius\">Island Fish Jasconius</a> to attack a person who controlled Mountains without worrying about his islandhome creature being buried.  And you could do all that without ever leaving blue!</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '363968'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (2/16/2014 8:15:12 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
